    public abstract static class IloCplex.QualityType
extends java.lang.Object
    This class contains symbolic names for IloCplex solution qualities. An instance of IloNumVar (or IloFloatVar or IloIntVar) or an instance of IloRange will be part of the qualities with names starting with Max. For these qualities, the variable or range returned is the first variable or range that attains the associated quality value.
